snippet.title: Panomino Gameplay Trailer (Alpha)
snippet.description:
Welcome to Panomino, the rogue-like deck-building falling-block puzzle-game!

Free alpha download available now for Windows:
https://snail-dream.itch.io/panomino

More updates coming soon.  Have fun!
